Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个月的部费  买完新枕头就用光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这枕头原来真是用部费买的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不愿意让你拿我的甜心代用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这俩男生真是令人伤脑筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,罪魁祸首…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我捏我捏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,宇佐美学姐好狠毒!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没有新的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但隔壁的储藏室里好像有个老的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁那是我们社团的储藏室吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我入部的时候  就已经基本不使用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,梦子老师或许不知道拿哪一把钥匙开门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就问问小山老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,…喂  你们干什么呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这门真是不太好开…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…就这点程度  根本不算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,分明喘得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,进去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,空间大概是活动室的一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,窗户也不方便打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  日光灯也打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还是趁早赶紧找到它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,画得真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  好好找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这漫画真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我小学时候读过的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了  找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜托你们关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得好紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你这副得意的表情是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这根本不算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先别提这个  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是和内卷同处一室…你也可千万别因此失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,失控?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀…门一关就变热了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是得通通风才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得紧也不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,居然这么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是是  是我小看你了  对不起  行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该说你孱弱无力  骨瘦如柴  面色苍白!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…你没说得这么严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  既然要道歉  就得更加有诚意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这箱子上写着「石膏像」三个字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊  宇佐美同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  快来开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,比一开始卡得更紧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,应该得怪你当时锤了一下门吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?  又成我的错了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我脸上沾了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好近!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…呼出的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,轻叩着我的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是可蕾特同学的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,学姐他们回去了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让她把老师叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学  听得见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这扇门打不开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天色这么晚了  我也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  手机呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没戏  在包里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要到放学时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷…如  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有人注意到我们  该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,既然门打不开  也只得维持现状了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的情况就是在这里住一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(686.997,572.644)\frz248.5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs60\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(691.497,611.644)\frz250.7}··
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办  如果继续变冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别突然这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?  很暖和吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你从刚才开始就在说些什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天已经黑透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么蹲在角落里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  怎么可能没感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在慌死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…在这又小又黑的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,直到明早  都得二人…独处…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,会起灰的  别打滚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学你没事吧  刚才就怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩得在这儿过一晚哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,都开始胡思乱想那种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,部长说的那句话还怎么反驳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,内…内卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我可是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给你看看我家甜心的厉害之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,摁下这个按钮  眼睛就会发光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  真亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这还是我第一次觉得内卷你的手办厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做的话  或许会让夜值巡逻的老师注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是又得好好巡逻才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊  梦子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  果然还是太黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那道光是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没人在才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,记得是这间来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才听到什么声音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你也听到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪之类的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是以前部员的纪念照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?  是照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  窗户这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像是一张脸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说过让你别吓唬我了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再这样我就把这个给折断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,比妖怪还可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你还来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吓唬你啦  你看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这里应该是这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是门吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从位置上看  另一边就是活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  你把那边的箱子移开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  原来这里相连在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好可蕾特同学没有把门锁上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果就那样待了一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他们以后会怎么捉弄我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了石膏像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搬石膏像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈打了好多通电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老师  您为何会在这种地方睡觉呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是现在还是以前都会有人对石膏像涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz278\pos(275.997,206.644)}贤弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz262\pos(922.497,290.644)}大哥哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz334\pos(275.997,307.144)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\pos(881.997,383.644)\frz336.9}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和短发波波头合起来就是…波啵午安!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧  很有趣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这本漫画也好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  这本我也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这本很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,女主角有超能力的那一部对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀技非常帅气  像这样…啪啪噼里啪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这间隐藏房间真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,既可以尽情看漫画又能够放松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你随时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看起来聊得很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做功课  所以可以请你们安静一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  功课在家里做不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们安静一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.17,Comment,,0,0,0,,你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我不就不知道你们在做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?  那当然是在看漫画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太安静的话总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什么夹在漫画里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宝物的所在之处?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给未来的美术部员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}俺有一宝贝疙瘩  就藏在咱校园里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,吾有秘宝  藏于黉门之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}看你们能解开谜题  去挖出宝贝不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,望尔等窥破机关以继承秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}希望俺这宝贝能找个好人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,若蒙菩萨心肠者得之  善哉善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  是寻宝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要玩玩看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我要玩  我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来刚好宇佐美同学就自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也能够方便她集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们赶快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到了休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在刚好是休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「离开活动室并前往绅士的小屋」上面这么写
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,绅士的小屋是指哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是脑筋急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一提暗号2是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「前往从绅士的小屋的窗户看得见的这个地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得至少是有窗户的房间才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  是指男厕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,的确很「绅士」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这里就麻烦内卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为身为淑女的我们是不能进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  淑女?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是了个是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是了个是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从窗户看得见的这的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一封奇怪的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也没什么特别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(832.5,990)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1027.5,990)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子想出来也不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候就是普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方  这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(994.5,990)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是「这」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1140,990)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  确实是这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同学  下个提示是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号3 「找出字母」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?  就这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,问题来了  登登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里来看的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是U
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行  伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我脑筋急转弯淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个  暗号4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「从找到的字母的末端开始  前进?步」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,「?步」?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,U的末端是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,步数是从1853到1890的向日葵的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道答案是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  还不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给一个提示  给一个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她很享受谜题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,提示  这是关于梵高的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(780,990)}Gogh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是什么来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}注：日语中「梵高」和「五步」的发音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,1步  2步  3步  4步  5步!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉不是美术部员也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…内卷你来告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是1853出生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,1890过世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他是荷兰的画家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,画家?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说暗号4的答案是梵高画过的向日葵的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有1幅烧毁了  但是一共有7幅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是7步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密宝物一定就在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  无论怎么努力  这里也不像是能挖的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么能挖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1065,990)}冈格尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,出现吧  永恒之枪!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:35.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}注：Gungnir  冈格尼尔  北欧神话中主神奥丁所使用的武器  是矮人族用世界之树的树枝打造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好短!  永恒之枪好短!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  凭我的魔力这就是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来就只有前端而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有写古文字吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错  毕竟是永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,随便丢也能挖?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,行了别闹了  好了别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,体力劳动就交给就交给内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好像挖到什么坚硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒之枪也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我们就来进行开封仪式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,无论有什么  都由我们三等分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我不是美术部员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是我们三人找到的  这是当然的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们重要的冒险证明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,色情…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,死零之书对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,各位也有在勤奋作画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀?  部长呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原来在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来…那边的房间有很多书对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我帮忙找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  这个美术部大有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,魔导书和再次的散步  敬请期待
